{"tid":1715597,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【男子闖幼兒園噴腐蝕液體釀54傷】","createTime":"2019-11-13T06:33:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T06:36:52.000Z","uid":2429,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"cf8118c805697dd46965e2ef567baae6e4a38f2c","tid":1715597,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T06:33:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/265944843550009/posts/2322451024566037/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F265944843550009%2Fposts%2F2322451024566037%2F&d=lZ7jQHZQyV3jEURUmMbLaadOOFpqpiAZGwRsEzlRJXk%3D&h=56cc7a6b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/265944843550009/posts/2322451024566037/</a><br />\n<br />\n【男子闖幼兒園噴腐蝕液體釀54傷】<br />\n<br />\n雲南開遠市周一下午，一個男人剪斷一間幼兒園的鐵絲網圍牆，爬入幼兒園後，向師生噴射俗稱「燒鹼」的高腐蝕性液體氫氧化鈉。<br />\n<br />\n事件造成48人輕傷、4人中度受傷及2人重傷，男子當場被公安拘捕。官方通報指男子由於自小家庭離異，加上工作不順利，出於厭世和報復社會的心態犯案。<br />\n<br />\n#報復社會<br />\n#腐蝕液體<br />\n#有線中國組<br />\n<br />\n支那人唔敢反抗淨係敢恰弱者。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eba54e5d91ba46890ae825eae7c23036248d76f1","tid":1715597,"uid":257622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T06:36:52.000Z","msg":"懦弱嘅人只敢對婦儒下手"}]}